title: Start Menu Alternatives April 2016
description:
Start Menu Alternatives April 2016

A compilation of start menu replacements for Windows 7 / 8 / 8.1 / 10 which allows you to boot directly to the Windows desktop.

Included in this release (24-04-2016):

- Start is Back+ for Windows 8.1 v1.7.5		- Homepage: http://startisback.com/
- Stardock Start8 for Windows 8.1 v1.56		- Homepage: http://www.stardock.com/products/start8/
- Start is Back++ for Windows 10 v1.2.1		- Homepage: http://startisback.com/
- Stardock Start10 for Windows 10 v1.10		- Homepage: http://www.stardock.com/products/start10/
- Classic Shell	v4.2.5				- Homepage: http://www.classicshell.net/
- IObit Start Menu 8 v3.0.0.0			- Homepage: http://www.iobit.com/en/iobitstartmenu8.php
- ViStart v8.1 Build 5208			- Homepage: http://lee-soft.com/vistart/
- Start Menu X Free v5.85			- Homepage: http://www.startmenux.com/index.html

Note about Classic Shell:
- The installer enabled is in English.
- To install it in your language, explore the folder and run the adequat installer.
- All available languages are provided.

- All programs included are pre-activated or free of charge.
- All programs in this release are safe.
- If your antivirus complains about a program, this is a false positive.
- If you have suggestions, please submit.
- If you don't like it, please don't use it.

Release Date: 25-04-2016
Interface language: English (programs are multilingual when available)
Size: 96.7 MB
